{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 200°C. Grease a casserole dish (30 cm x 20 cm) and set aside.","Place a ceramic or glass bowl onto mixing bowl lid, then weigh red lentils into it. Add enough water to cover and set lentils aside to soak for 2 hours.","Place Parmesan cheese in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>10 sec\/speed 9<\/nobr>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place olive oil, onion, garlic and red pepper in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","Add tomatoes (including liquid) and mix <nobr>2 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add red wine, oregano, ginger, salt and pepper then cook <nobr>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Place Varoma dish into position, then arrange aubergine slices into it to ensure steam can circulate freely. Secure Varoma lid and steam <nobr>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Remove Varoma and set aubergine aside.","Drain lentils through simmering basket. Add drained lentils and cook <nobr>7 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Transfer steamed aubergine slices into base of prepared casserole dish, then top with lentil mixture in mixing bowl. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place butter, milk and flour in mixing bowl then cook <nobr>8 min\/90°C\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Add 60 g reserved Parmesan cheese and mix <nobr>5 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Transfer cheese sauce into casserole dish and sprinkle with remaining 60 g reserved Parmesan. Bake for 30 minutes (200°C) or until top is lightly golden brown. Cut moussaka into squares and serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["40 g butter, plus extra for greasing","200 g red lentils","120 g Parmesan cheese, crust removed and cut into cubes (3 cm)","50 g olive oil","1 onion (approx. 150 g), quartered","3 garlic cloves","1 red pepper, deseeded and cut into pieces","400 g tinned chopped tomatoes (including liquid)","120 g red wine","1 sprig fresh oregano, leaves only","1 tsp ground ginger","2 tsp fine sea salt","½ tsp ground black pepper","1 aubergine (approx. 550 g), cut into slices (1 cm)","500 g whole milk","40 g spelt flour"]}],"id":"r123534","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-ms2LJBFqipM\/XZVQpl7vHaI\/AAAAAAAAdD8\/r-Vaxmx0O_wu4DiE_sIg-Fr6vCkiMWGQwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Tgf1kXK0zPR-eFRp.png","title":"Lentil Moussaka","publishedAt":"2017-03-20T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"20 g","fat":"25 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"29 g","calories":"1863 kJ \/ 443 kcal"},"usefulItems":"casserole dish (30 x 20 cm), bowl, oven","basicInfo":["easy","25m","3h 30m","6 portions"]}